### Notation

- `[pause]` - 0.5 second pause
- `[long pause]` - 1 second pause
- `*word*` - Emphasize this word
- `[slower]` - Reduce pace for following section
- `[normal]` - Return to normal pace
- `{pronunciation}` - Phonetic guide (e.g., "GUI {goo-ee}")

### Tone

- Conversational, not robotic
- Teacher explaining to students
- Confident but approachable
- Enthusiastic about the subject

